headline: Trane Technologies Unveils Industry's First Comprehensive Thermal Management System Reference Design for Gigawatt Scale NVIDIA AI Factories
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, October 28, 2025--Trane Technologies (NYSE:TT), a global climate innovator, today announced the launch of the industry’s first comprehensive thermal management system reference design, specifically engineered for the NVIDIA Omniverse DSX Blueprint for gigawatt-scale AI data centers. headline: Carrier Global (CARR) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Carrier Global (CARR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +21.82% and +0.93%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
